          (i) <m>A=\begin{bmatrix}1 \amp 2 \amp 1 \\ 3 \amp 4 \amp 2 \\ 3 \amp 3 \amp -1 \end{bmatrix}</m> (ii) <m>A = \begin{bmatrix}0 \amp 2 \amp 0 \\ 2 \amp 0 \amp 2 \\ 0 \amp 0 \amp 2 \end{bmatrix}</m> (iii)
